{"word":"παρακούω","slug":"παρακούω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παραϰούω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀκούω\">ἀκούω</a></el>] ‘hear without paying close attention’, <b>ignore<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on disobedience <b><a href='B:470 18:17'>Mt 18:17</a>; <a href='B:490 5:5'>Lk 5:5</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on dismissing what is heard<b> <a href='B:480 5:36'>Mk 5:36</a>;</b> but some prefer <b>overhear</b> for this passage. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρακολουθέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παρακύπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}